# Only the Next.js web app needs to reach Vercel. Exclude the heavy non-JS build domains
# and local build artifacts (they took the upload to 1.2GB).
#
# LEADING SLASH IS REQUIRED: an unanchored pattern like `circuits` matches at ANY depth and
# would also drop public/circuits/*.zkey (the proving artifacts the browser actually fetches).
# Anchor everything to the repo root.
**/node_modules
.next
.git
/contracts
/circuits
/tests
/docs
**/target
*.log
